rdiscd (0.5-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * Also install rdiscd-mkaddress.
  * Refer to RFC 7217 in description.
  * Clean up / modernize packaging.
    - Remove pointless Build-Depends.
    - Upgrade to modern copyright file format.
    - Switch to quilt source format.
    - Use pristine-tar.
  * ifupdown hook: read config value from file if value prefixed with '<'.

 -- Andrew Ayer <agwa@andrewayer.name>  Sat, 04 Oct 2014 15:14:15 -0700

